### ============================================================================
### CONTENT — Blog, FAQ, Translations, Newsletter, Contact
### ============================================================================

### ─── Blog Posts — /api/v1/blog-posts ───────────────────────

### List blog posts (paginated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/blog-posts?page=0&size=20

### Get blog post by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/blog-posts/{{blogPostId}}

### Create blog post
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/blog-posts
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Travel Health Tips for West Africa",
  "slug": "travel-health-tips-west-africa",
  "excerpt": "Essential health advice for travelers to West Africa.",
  "content": "When traveling to West Africa, it's important to...",
  "category": "Travel Tips",
  "readTime": 5,
  "publishedAt": "2025-06-01T10:00:00",
  "isPublished": true,
  "userId": {{userId}}
}

### Update blog post
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/blog-posts/{{blogPostId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated: Travel Health Tips for West Africa",
  "excerpt": "Updated essential health advice.",
  "isPublished": true,
  "userId": {{userId}}
}

### Delete blog post
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/blog-posts/{{blogPostId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### ─── FAQ Items — /api/v1/faq-items ─────────────────────────

### List FAQ items (paginated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/faq-items?page=0&size=20

### Get FAQ item by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/faq-items/{{faqItemId}}

### Create FAQ item
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/faq-items
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "What vaccinations do I need for Nigeria?",
  "answer": "Yellow fever vaccination is required. Hepatitis A, Typhoid, and Meningitis are recommended.",
  "category": "Vaccinations",
  "position": 1,
  "isActive": true
}

### Update FAQ item
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/faq-items/{{faqItemId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "What vaccinations do I need for Nigeria?",
  "answer": "Updated: Yellow fever, Hepatitis A, Typhoid, and Meningitis are recommended.",
  "category": "Vaccinations",
  "position": 1,
  "isActive": true
}

### Delete FAQ item
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/faq-items/{{faqItemId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### ─── Translations — /api/v1/translations ───────────────────

### List translations (paginated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/translations?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get translation by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/translations/{{translationId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Create translation
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/translations
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "locale": "fr",
  "key": "onboarding.welcome",
  "value": "Bienvenue sur TMAG"
}

### Update translation
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/translations/{{translationId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "locale": "fr",
  "key": "onboarding.welcome",
  "value": "Bienvenue sur Travel Medicine Advisory Global"
}

### Delete translation
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/translations/{{translationId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### ─── Newsletter — /api/v1/newsletter ───────────────────────

### Subscribe to newsletter
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/newsletter/subscribe
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "subscriber@example.com",
  "name": "Subscriber Name"
}

### ─── Contact — /api/v1/contact ─────────────────────────────

### Submit contact form
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/contact
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "subject": "Partnership inquiry",
  "message": "We are interested in partnering with TMAG for corporate travel health.",
  "inquiryType": "PARTNERSHIP"
}
